ENTREZ_GENE_ID: NCBI Entrez Gene database id of intended siRNA target gene
NCBI_GENE_SYMBOL: Official symbol of target NCBI Gene Id
MIGRATION_AVERAGE_NORMALISED_TO_MOCK_HMB: Migration data for each replicate normalised to Mock then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates.
MIGRATION_AVERAGE_NORMALISED_TO_MOCK_HDL: Migration data for each replicate normalised to Mock then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates.
AVERAGE_CELL_COUNT_HMBEC: Cell count data for each replicate then averaged the values across the 2 replicates.
AVERAGE_CELL_COUNT_HDLEC: Cell count data for each replicate then averaged the values across the 2 replicates.
MIGRATION_BIN_HMBEC: Migration binning classification: IMPAIRED (low migration score): value < 0.65 NC (no change): value > 0.65
MIGRATION_BIN_HDLEC: Migration binning classification: IMPAIRED (low migration score): value < 0.65 NC (no change): value > 0.65
AVERAGE_CELL_COUNT_BIN_HMBEC: Cell count binning classification: LOW_CELL_COUNT (low cell number): value < 2500 NC (no change): value > 2500
AVERAGE_CELL_COUNT_BIN_HDLEC: Cell count binning classification: LOW_CELL_COUNT (low cell number): value < 3300 NC (no change): value > 3300
DOMINANT_CELL_ACTIVITY_BIN: Dominant cell type migration binning classification: BEC_DOMINANT : if IMPAIRED in MIGRATION_BIN_HMBEC but NOT in MIGRATION_BIN_HDLEC LEC_DOMINANT : if IMPAIRED in MIGRATION_BIN_HDLEC but NOT in MIGRATION_BIN_HMBEC COMMON : if IMPAIRED in MIGRATION_BIN_HDLEC AND in MIGRATION_BIN_HMBEC NC (no change) : if NC in both cell types.
EXCLUDED_WELL_FLAG_SUMMARY: Wells are flagged with ONE REP when one of the two replicate wells were excluded
